<h3 id="add">Create a new category</h3>

<p>
	If you want to add a <i>root</i> level category or create the very first category:
	<ol>
		<li>Select LiveCart on the category tree</li>
		<li>Click the "Add new sub-category" link right below the category tree.
	</ol>
</p>

<p>
	If you want to add a <i>sub-category</i> for any existing category:
	<ol>
		<li>Select the desired category on the category tree.</li>
		<li>Click "Add new sub-category".</li>
	</ol>
</p>

<h3 id="move">Move category</h3>

<p>You can move categories by dragging and dropping them directly in the category tree:</p>

<ol>
	<li>Select a category on the category tree.</li>
	<li>While holding the category drag it up or down to place into appropriate category:</li>
	<img src="image/doc/categories/move_contents.bmp">
</ol>

<p class="note"><strong>Note</strong>: All of the contents are moved together with the category, including products, attributes, images, etc.</p>


<h3 id="remove">Remove a category</h3>

<p>To remove a category <strong>including all its subcategories and products</strong> select a category and click 
"Remove selected category" below the category tree: </p>
<p><img src="image/doc/categories/remove.bmp"></p>



<h3 id="reorder">Reorder categories</h3>

<p>To change category order:</p>

<ol>
	<li>Select a category on the category tree.</li>
	<li>Use "Move category up" and "Move category down" to move the category up or down.</li>
	<img src="image/doc/categories/up_down.bmp">
</ol>




